# Tech Stack

- Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, React, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion.

# Design System & UI/UX

- Aesthetic: Strictly enforce a dark, minimalist, and modern UI aesthetic.
- The design must be high-contrast and highly legible for delivery riders operating outdoors at night.
- Avoid unnecessary visual clutter; prioritize speed, typography, and clean spacing.

# Code Style

- Use strict TypeScript typing. Interfaces/Types should be declared clearly for API responses.
- Use functional components and React Hooks. Keep components modular and single-purpose.
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes exclusively. Group classes logically.
- Utilize Next.js Server Components where possible for performance, and Supabase client-side fetching for real-time UI updates.
